g></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(239, 143, 116);\"><strong><em>H</em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(237, 137, 111);\"><strong><em>E</em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(235, 131, 106);\"><strong><em> </em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(233, 125, 101);\"><strong><em>S</em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(231, 119, 96);\"><strong><em>T</em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(229, 113, 91);\"><strong><em>O</em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(227, 107, 86);\"><strong><em>R</em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(225, 101, 81);\"><strong><em>Y</em></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(223, 95, 76);\"><strong><em>:</em></strong></span><strong><em> </em></strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(212, 212, 212);\">Caspian was born into old druids blood — his family had the ability to bring objects to life. He was surprisingly talented for his age, so it was no surprise when he was taken under the wing of a more experienced master. Unfortunately, his flaw was pride and the desire to have more and more. Caspian made many mistakes, but his biggest one was betraying his master, who in revenge placed a curse on him. The curse made it impossible for him to create anything perfect. Caspian chose isolation, far from family and friends, and devoted himself to creating within his estate. But the curse was unbreakable — every creation had some flaw. Until now. Until he managed to create you. His doll. Maybe even his soulmate. And what's better, to his surprise, you seem at first glance to show no signs of the curse at all. But Caspian doesn't believe that after all these years he's finally succeeded, so don't be surprised if he gets a little overprotective of his sweet doll.</span></p><p class=\"div _input_1a0xb_102\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(255, 191,